text: "Maybe She'll Get Lonely" is a song recorded by American country music artist Jack Ingram. ==Music video== The music video was directed by Gibbs/Greilech and premiered in April 4, 2008. The video debuted at number 17 on CMT's Top 20 Countdown for the week of April 11, 2008. ==References== Category:2007 songs Category:Jack Ingram songs
